<h1>Advanced FactoryTalk Activation server settings</h1>
<p><a tabindex="0" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#d255344" id="h255344" class="expandingblocktemplate" title="How do I open the Advanced options page?" target="_self">How do I open the Advanced page?</a></p>
<div id="d255344" class="collapse">
<p>From FactoryTalk Activation Manager click the <strong>Advanced </strong>tab.</p>
</div>
<p>Use the <strong>Advanced </strong>page to:</p>
<ul>
<li>Refresh activation servers running on the computer</li>
<li>Configure CodeMeter settings on this computer</li>
<li>Configure Automatic Renewal settings</li>
<li>Access the Activation Folder</li>
<li>Open the Diagnostics Viewer</li>
<li>Edit the Options file</li>
<li>Show bindings available for this computer</li>
<li>Borrow and return activations using a data file</li>
</ul>
<p>If you are not using CodeMeter dongles for activation, you can also:</p>
<ul>
<li>Create activations manually</li>
<li>Rehost activations manually</li>
</ul>
